Class Critter

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Subject
      • models.Critter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DrawableEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Critter_Cyan, Critter_Orange, Critter_Pink, Critter_Red, Critter_White, Critter_Yellow

    public abstract class Critter
extends Subject
implements DrawableEntity
    Critter abstract class from which all critters extend. Has certain attributes and methods including taking a step, getting damaged, etc.
